under act of March 81873 HEARSTS SUNDAY AMERICAN and THE ATLANTA GEORGIAN wHI be mailed to subscribers anywhere in the United States anaoa and Mexico one month for 160 three months for II 75 six months for f 3 50 and one year for 1700 change of address made a often as deaired Foreign subscription rates on a plication JUDGE HILL WRITES A SPLENDID EDITORIALThat All the People Should Read Study and Try to Remember Judge Benjamin H Hills letter addressed to Governor Sla ton is so able timely and carefully thought out that we republish it in its entirely to day in these columns It is a SPLENDID EDITORIALthe best perhaps that has appeared in The Geor gian in many a day The capitalized words are ours We wish to emphasize them and we ask our readers to study them and try to grasp their full meaning JUDGE HILLS LETTER His Excellency John M Slaton Governor Atlanta Ga My Dear Governor Slaton J cannot content myself with merely a formal expression of appreciation of"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-05-22T12:58:29.408Z", "group": ["ndnp/gu", "digital-library-of-georgia-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn89053729/1913-11-04/ed-1/?sp=16", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_kesil_ver01:data:sn89053729:00393344581:1913110401:0116/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=260&w=214", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_kesil_ver01:data:sn89053729:00393344581:1913110401:0116/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=520&w=428", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_kesil_ver01:data:sn89053729:00393344581:1913110401:0116/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1040&w=856", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/gu/batch_gu_kesil_ver01/data/sn89053729/00393344581/1913110401/0116.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 16, "language": ["english"], "location": ["fulton county", "fulton", "georgia", "atlanta", "united states"], "loc